        Invoke a revision or version of a rule service

        Invokes the deployed rule service with the specified revision or version and a specified vocabulary input.<br>If *RuleServiceRevision* is specified, the highest semantic version of the revision is invoked.<br>

        200 - Successful invocation of rule service.

        400 - Bad Request.

        404 - Object not found. The entity you are trying to invoke does not exist.

        Parameters:
        body - JSON payload of the input to rule servie execution.

        RuleServiceResult
